name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: If you’re donating money through crowdfunding, thank you for your generosity. This publication has tips on protecting yourself and the $ you’re donating. For any questions, the Charities Division of my office is here to help.  https://t.co/fj2XgWNv0j

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: There are broader lessons here for everyone. If you’re raising $ thru crowdfunding for a charitable (not personal) purpose, there are laws you need to comply with even if you’re not a nonprofit or 501c3. Read this to know your legal responsibilities.  https://t.co/Srqcm8t8Yk

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: Philando Castile cared deeply about the children he served & the children loved him back. Not using every dollar raised in his name to help children was an insult to his legacy & his loved ones. I’ve made sure all the $ raised will now help those kids.  https://t.co/TGLxdfAJC6

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: There are real people and stories behind the 5,550 MNs lost to the opioid crisis. The money should go where the pain is.  Passing HF 4265 will provide relief by getting $300 million to Minnesota communities for treatment, abatement, and prevention where it’s needed most. #mnleg  https://t.co/hfew9RK9GX

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: No amount of money can ever make up for the death & destruction that opioid companies caused in MN but we’ve still held them accountable.   Passing HF 4265 brings relief by getting $300 million to MN communities for treatment, abatement & prevention where it’s needed most. #mnleg  https://t.co/USoSJnD5ux

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: I’ve stood up for kids before: I asked FB to ditch plans for Insta for kids & joined national investigations of Insta & TikTok for promoting their platforms despite known harms. It’s all our job to help the youngest & most vulnerable Minnesotans live w dignity, safety & respect.

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: The harms of social media use on children are real, up to & incl bullying & self-harm. I joined a bipartisan group of 44 AGs asking TikTok & Snapchat to do more to let parents protect their kids. I’ll keep using my office to make sure our kids are safe.  https://t.co/s0xRAZ6AKM

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: More detail about the settlement & link to original lawsuit here. Thanks very much to Philando’s mother Valerie Castile for all her support along the way and for being a powerful moral leader.  https://t.co/aAakSXjW1S

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: Last yr I sued Philando Feeds the Children, a project that was supposed to honor Philando Castile by paying off lunch debts of St Paul Public Schools kids—but $120K was not put to that purpose. name: Attorney General Keith Ellison

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: Remember the Mpls landlord I prosecuted who made tenants live w infestations “of Biblical plague proportions”? Today, the court awarded us $1M in prosecution costs. Landlords who abuse tenants, take note: we’ll hold you accountable w all the tools we have.  https://t.co/t3eyP9ipEu

name: Attorney General Keith Ellison
tweet: Existing laws allow the oppty for predatory bad actors to take advtge of accident victims or dependents. These victims deserve to be treated fairly.
